Trademark Application Details





The mark consists of the letter "D" appearing next to and facing of a backwards appearing letter "D" with the number "2" overlaid horizontally across both "D" letters, resulting in and inter-locking "D2D" design appearing directly above the wording "DOOR 2 DOOR" appearing directly above the wording "STRATEGIES".
Mark For: D2D DOOR 2 DOOR STRATEGIES® trademark registration is intended to cover the category of promoting the interests of political candidates and community development by means of public advocacy. [all]
>Color is not claimed as a feature of the mark.
